---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout>
  <h2>Welcome to Voidless Tale</h2>
  <p>A 2D pixel-art action RPG where Heaven and Hell collide. Absorb the powers of your foes or loot their treasures as you uncover your forgotten sins.</p>
  <section>
    <h3>Highlights</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Dual realms of Heaven and Hell, each with eight unique domains.</li>
      <li>Loot vs. Absorb mechanic for deep customization.</li>
      <li>Level 1&ndash;1000 progression leading to Demigod transformation.</li>
      <li>Full mod support and the Voidless Smith weapon editor.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
